* PORTS USED *

80   - Perlbal ( reproxies to httpd.pl )
2022 - Perlbal cometd connector service ( event server connects here, also telnet and issue commands )
8065 - Perlbal manager ( telnet to and issue commands )
8021 - httpd.pl ( simple web server, can be replaced by cometd http server soon )
8080 - Cometd http server ( test server to use apache benchmark against )
5000 - Cometd manager ( telnet to and issue commands ), use telnet
8000 - Simple test server for the event system, use telnet
